Need a VM with gcloud and other tools pre-installed

sh-keygen -t rsa -f ~/.ssh/gcp -C dhariwal@pythian.com

Local gcloud setup
==================
- first setup the google cloud sdk https://cloud.google.com/sdk/docs/quickstart-mac-os-x
		mv google-cloud-sdk-158.0.0-darwin-x86_64.tar.gz ~
		cd ~
		tar -xvzf google-cloud-sdk-158.0.0-darwin-x86_64.tar.gz
		sudo ./google-cloud-sdk/install.sh

- Initialize the SDK
		sudo gcloud init

- Test
		sudo gcloud auth list
		sudo gcloud config list

		